premise_source_doc_sentence: Robert Elmer Balaban  (  born August 16 , 1945  )  is an American actor , author , producer , and director .
He was one of the producers nominated for the Academy Award for Best Picture for Gosford Park  (  2001  )  , in which he also appeared .

Producer/director Burt Balaban  (  1922-1965  )  was the son of Barney Balaban , president of Paramount Pictures from 1936 to 1964 , and cousin of actor Bob Balaban , of Close Encounters of the Third Kind  (  1977  )  and Gosford Park  (  2001  )  .
Bob Balaban  (  1945 -  )  , American actor and director  (  related to the founders of Balaban and Katz  )
Development on Gosford Park began in 1999 , when Bob Balaban asked Altman if they could develop a film together .

Grant , Derek Jacobi , Kelly Macdonald , Helen Mirren , Jeremy Northam , Clive Owen , Ryan Phillippe , Maggie Smith , Kristin Scott Thomas , and Emily Watson .
